  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish-Click Squad!  is a casual multiplayer idler where you purchase various aquatic creatures and nurture them to maturity with your friends through clicking and touching earning coins and rewards to unlock more fish and idle features!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is nothing happier than slacking with friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/54da8452bc975680560bd251f2638984.poster.avif?t=1771003994\" width=800 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/54da8452bc975680560bd251f2638984.webm?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/54da8452bc975680560bd251f2638984.mp4?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up and slack together with your friend! You may join a friend's room or a stranger's room, and enjoy touching your fish in spare time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/f0d7d06e67ef614e5904b63f85669b6d.avif?t=1771003994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras_big/f0d7d06e67ef614e5904b63f85669b6d.avif?t=1771003994 width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy some fish fry or some strange young aquatic creatures to start your fish-farming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/b77de937bb0e4b35a6170d1a637a4051.avif?t=1771003994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras_big/b77de937bb0e4b35a6170d1a637a4051.avif?t=1771003994 width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every click can gradually make your fish grow bigger and become more visible(+1s)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/9794684224f5334e03c5d991b2a7baee.poster.avif?t=1771003994\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/9794684224f5334e03c5d991b2a7baee.webm?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/9794684224f5334e03c5d991b2a7baee.mp4?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After touching the fish to fully-visible, remember to use the fishnet to get what you nurtured.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/e3d1228a2a06ed75bd854c564639980c.avif?t=1771003994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras_big/e3d1228a2a06ed75bd854c564639980c.avif?t=1771003994 width=800 height=422 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fully-touched fish got by fishnet will swim freely in the viewing area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/22c6fca6f482288d61a39c45e924da55.avif?t=1771003994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras_big/22c6fca6f482288d61a39c45e924da55.avif?t=1771003994 width=800 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/a29b6b6dc3fb713aadff526b02b5e9a1.poster.avif?t=1771003994\" width=800 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/a29b6b6dc3fb713aadff526b02b5e9a1.webm?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/a29b6b6dc3fb713aadff526b02b5e9a1.mp4?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are too busy at work don't have time to slack, you may hire our cute cat divers to nurture your cute fish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/168c660c4ee20f53e677b056b164d4cb.avif?t=1771003994\" width=242 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to freely explore more features in game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/c2fa45082e1ddd549aa5fc484196f2df.avif?t=1771003994\" width=502 height=314 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish-Click Squad!  is a casual multiplayer idler where you purchase various aquatic creatures and nurture them to maturity with your friends through clicking and touching earning coins and rewards to unlock more fish and idle features!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is nothing happier than slacking with friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/54da8452bc975680560bd251f2638984.poster.avif?t=1771003994\" width=800 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/54da8452bc975680560bd251f2638984.webm?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/54da8452bc975680560bd251f2638984.mp4?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up and slack together with your friend! You may join a friend's room or a stranger's room, and enjoy touching your fish in spare time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/f0d7d06e67ef614e5904b63f85669b6d.avif?t=1771003994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras_big/f0d7d06e67ef614e5904b63f85669b6d.avif?t=1771003994 width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy some fish fry or some strange young aquatic creatures to start your fish-farming.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/b77de937bb0e4b35a6170d1a637a4051.avif?t=1771003994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.s