ideo class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/a29b6b6dc3fb713aadff526b02b5e9a1.poster.avif?t=1771003994\" width=800 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/a29b6b6dc3fb713aadff526b02b5e9a1.webm?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/a29b6b6dc3fb713aadff526b02b5e9a1.mp4?t=1771003994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are too busy at work don't have time to slack, you may hire our cute cat divers to nurture your cute fish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/168c660c4ee20f53e677b056b164d4cb.avif?t=1771003994\" width=242 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to freely explore more features in game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982100/extras/c2fa45082e1ddd549aa5fc484196f2df.avif?t=1771003994\" width=502 height=314 /></span></p>",
